git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle
cp vim/.vimrc ~/
:BundleInstall

Windows Tips:
    Adding open in new tab setting to registory:
        HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Applications\gvim.exe\shell\edit\command "D:\program\Vim\vim74\gvim.exe" -p --remote-tab-silent "%1"

About .dir_colors file:
Ubuntu use .dircolors not .dir_colors, so you need to rename it or edit .bashrc.
